casebody.data:
Monday, August 25, 1997

MOTION DOCKET

97-1101. In re Appeal of Citywide Ambulance Serv., Inc.

Franklin App. No. 96APE08-1119.

This cause is pending before the court as a discretionary appeal. Upon consideration of the joint motion for stay pending execution of settlement agreement,

IT IS ORDERED by the court that the motion for stay pending execution of settlement agreement be, and hereby is, granted, for a period of fourteen days from the date of this entry.
